channel.description: Resources Slides Video Script Hello and welcome to the week nine announcements video for CIS 527 and CC 510 in fall 2024. I’m coming to you this week from my office on campus because I’m on the road a little bit. Hopefully the video quality is not too bad and you can get everything that I need to get across in these announcements. So for this week you should be working on lab four.
